AlamoneMeetLines		0	$ 30	$ Ho, there! $
AlamoneMeetLines		1	$ 60	$ You're not a- Well, uh, I guess you are? $
AlamoneMeetLines		2	$ 69	$ You're not yearning for my faith anyways. $
AlamoneMeetLines		3	$ 60	$ Name's Alamone, Alamone Over Deep. $
AlamoneMeetLines		4	$ 110	$ See I figure I'm the last normal person up here, so how better to call myself? $
AlamoneMeetLines		5	$ 74	$ Anyways, I've got some gear, want to take a look? $

